                            <comment id="13966346" author="njiang" created="Fri, 11 Apr 2014 08:54:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The right syntax of bodyAs is &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt; ${bodyAs(type)} &lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;, current code don&apos;t check the rest string after bodyAs(type).&lt;br/&gt;
I will updated the code to check the rest string and throw the exception if the string is not empty.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13966455" author="njiang" created="Fri, 11 Apr 2014 12:46:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Applied the patch into camel master, camel-2.13.x and camel-2.12.x branches.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13966927" author="alanfoster" created="Fri, 11 Apr 2014 18:27:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=njiang&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;njiang&quot;&gt;njiang&lt;/a&gt; - For what it&apos;s worth, this problem is also apparent within the headerAs function -&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-xml&quot;&gt;            &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;setBody&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
                &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;simple&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;${headerAs(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;foo&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, String).test)}&lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/simple&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;span class=&quot;code-tag&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;/setBody&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Should I reopen, or create a different issue for this scenario?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13967385" author="njiang" created="Sat, 12 Apr 2014 04:05:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi Alan,&lt;br/&gt;
We need to fix the headerAs function at the same time.&lt;br/&gt;
You don&apos;t need to create a new JIRA, I can keep fixing the issue by using this JIRA number.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13967392" author="njiang" created="Sat, 12 Apr 2014 04:26:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed the patch to fix headerAs issue into master, camel-2.13.x and camel-2.12.x branches.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
